    "created_at": "2014-02-27T21:36:27Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-02-27T21:36:27Z",
    "body": "This is an important issue.  We need to be a little concerned about over-committing too many guarantees about our FFI and the ABI and data representations / compatibility in 1.0.\n\nIn any case, right now we are not going to guarantee that we will solve this particular problem for 1.0.\n\nP-high, but not 1.0.\n",
